,{"label":"Jn 2:21","book":"Jhn","chapter":2,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mrk:15:44","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Pilate was surprised that he was already dead. Summoning the centurion, he asked him whether he had already died. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mrk:15:45","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When he found out from the centurion, he gave the corpse to Joseph. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mrk:15:46","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"After he bought some linen cloth, Joseph took him down and wrapped him in the linen. Then he laid him in a tomb "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 5:28","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":28,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 11:38","book":"Jhn","chapter":11,"verse":38,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:29","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":29,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" cut out of the rock and rolled a stone "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 20:1","book":"Jhn","chapter":20,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" against the entrance to the tomb. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 5:28","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":28},{"label":"Jn 11:38","book":"Jhn","chapter":11,"verse":38},{"label":"Ac 13:29","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":29},{"label":"Jn 20:1","book":"Jhn","chapter":20,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mrk:15:47","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Mary Magdalene "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 27:61–66","book":"Mat","chapter":27,"verse":61,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 23:55–56","book":"Luk","chapter":23,"verse":55,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and Mary the mother of Joses were watching where he was laid."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 27:61–66","book":"Mat","chapter":27,"verse":61},{"label":"Lk 23:55–56","book":"Luk","chapter":23,"verse":55}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279628055}